    <item>
      <title>अग्नि-स्तम्भनादि</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/AgamaH/AryaH/hinduism/sAmya-vaiShamye/bases/1_observation/alaukika-kathAH/bhUta-niyamanam/agni-stambhanAdi/</link>
